<s> Dan, after our discussion today this idea gelled with me further when it connected to some discussion I had with the HTML WG last week and a question I asked there: 2. It would cool that if instead of an RDF application only accepting a particular syntax, it had a MANDATORY mechanism (i.e. XSLT) that enabled it to transform any XML to a suitable serialization prior to consumption.  </s>
