<s> Also, you mentioned the use of a profile, akin to what you've proposed in [1], but today we noted that we might want to have *more than* transform associated with any given XHTML document (one for yeilding the creative commons, another for the calendar, etc.), but you can only have one profile in the html:head element, right?  </s>
